Chase Manhattan Corp said ChaseTrans-Info, a subsidiary of its Chase Manhattan Bank N.A. unit,has bought Borg-Warner Corp's Traffic Services business,including an Illinois processing center, for an undisclosedsum.    Borg Warner Traffic Services provides freight billpre-audit, payment and information services to industry throughBorg-Warner Acceptance Corp.    Chase Trans-Info, which offers similar services, is now thelargest provider of information services for the transportationindustry. Reuter&#3;